sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
This action retrieves the completed order report by the order ID.

Inputs:

  • Order ID - ID of the order for which the report is to be fetched.
  • Format - Supported options are :
    • PDF
    • HTML
  • User ID - ID of the user for viewing the report.

Outputs:

  • Report Link - A downloadable link to the report.
  • Status - Will be set to "Success" if the request succeeds or "Error" if a failure occurs.
  • Error Message - Will be populated when the status is "Error".

Error Messages:

  • Provided Order ID is invalid or not found.
  • Provided User ID is incorrect/invalid or appears to be empty.
  • Either provided Order ID or User ID is invalid/incorrect.
  • Invalid username or password/token or the token has expired.
  • The user does not have sufficient permission to perform this action.

Additional Note:

  • The action returns success, even if the Format input is incorrect/invalid, hence please make sure you provide a correct value.
  • The Report Link available in the output is only accessible for Orders in 'Completed' state.
  • The Report Link available in the output is only accessible for Users with sufficient viewing rights.

To use this action, the corresponding First Advantage connection and credential must be created and associated with the First Advantage Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
